# gen74: chat contraction canonicalization. Common abbreviated forms
# are expanded to canonical spaced forms so existing parsers work.
# "sup" added to social.p0 as an opening marker.
> sup
< Hi there!
> whats 2 plus 2
< 4.
> what's 2 plus 2
< 4.
> whos a dog
< I don't know about dog.
> dont say that
< I don't understand that yet.
> whats parrot0
< parrot0 is parrot0.
# broader wellbeing patterns from social.p0
> how is your day going
< I'm well, thanks. How can I help?
> hows your day
< I'm well, thanks. How can I help?
